    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is designed to evaluate olanzapine compared to the metoclopramide in the treatment
      of break through emesis after prophylaxis with dexamethasone, 5-HT 3 receptor antagonists and
      aprepitant in patients receiving chemotherapy. Efficacy will be assessed using a modified
      MASCC questionaire with a visual analog scale.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
